---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import { FiTarget, FiUsers, FiHeart } from 'react-icons/fi';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Game da Mu - Technologiya"
  description="Koyi game da Technologiya da manufarmu na kawo sabbin labarai na fasaha a Hausa"
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-6">
        Game da Technologiya
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        Mafi kyawun wurin samun sabbin labarai game da wayoyi, manhajoji, da dabaru na fasaha a cikin Hausa
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      
      <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <FiTarget class="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
          Manufarmu
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Mu kawo sabbin labarai da kuma bayani game da fasaha a cikin Hausa don taimaka wa jama'armu su fahimci cigaban fasaha.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <FiUsers class="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
          Wane ne Muke?
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Mu ƙungiyar marubuta ne masu ƙaunar fasaha da kuma son kawo sabbin labarai zuwa ga masu magana da Hausa a duniya.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-8 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <FiHeart class="w-6 h-6 text-white" />
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
          Dalilinmu
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Muna son kowane mai magana da Hausa ya sami damar koyi da kuma fahimtar cigaban fasaha cikin harshensu.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none mb-12
                  prose-headings:text-gray-900 dark:prose-headings:text-gray-100
                  prose-p:text-gray-700 dark:prose-p:text-gray-300">
        
        <h2>Tarihin Mu</h2>
        <p>
          Technologiya ta fara ne a shekarar 2025 da manufar kawo sabbin labarai da bayani game da fasaha a cikin Hausa. 
          Mun gane cewa akwai babban buƙatar samun ingantattun labarai game da fasaha a cikin Hausa, saboda haka muka 
          ƙaddamar da wannan shafin.
        </p>

        <h2>Abin da Muke Yi</h2>
        <p>
          A Technologiya, muna ba da:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Labarai Na Wayoyi:</strong> Sabbin labarai game da wayoyi da na'urorin hannu</li>
          <li><strong>Bitar Kayayyaki:</strong> Bita mai zurfi na na'urorin fasaha</li>
          <li><strong>Koyarwar Manhajoji:</strong> Yadda ake amfani da manhajoji daban-daban</li>
          <li><strong>Dabaru da Shawarwari:</strong> Dabaru masu amfani don inganta amfani da fasaha</li>
          <li><strong>Koyarwa:</strong> Shirye-shiryen koyarwa step-by-step</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Manufofinmu</h2>
        <p>
          Muna da manufa ce ta:
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li>Zama mafi babban shafin labarai na fasaha a Hausa</li>
          <li>Taimaka wa jama'a su fahimci cigaban fasaha</li>
          <li>Kara yawan masu magana da Hausa da ke amfani da fasaha</li>
          <li>Gina ƙungiya mai ƙarfi ta masu ƙaunar fasaha</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Tuntuɓe Mu</h2>
        <p>
          Muna son jin ra'ayinku! Idan kuna da wata tambaya ko shawarwari, za ku iya tuntuɓe mu ta:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Email: info@technologiya.com</li>
          <li>Facebook: @TechnologiyaHausa</li>
          <li>Twitter: @TechNaHausa</li>
          <li>WhatsApp: +234 XXX XXX XXXX</li>
        </ul>

      </div>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <div class="mt-16 p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-800 rounded-xl text-center text-white">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
          Zo Ku Kasance Cikin Ƙungiyarmu
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg mb-6 opacity-90">
          Ku biyo mu a kafofin watsa labarun don samun sabbin labarai da kuma bayani game da fasaha
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <a 
            href="https://facebook.com" 
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="px-6 py-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
          >
            Bi Mu a Facebook
          </a>
          <a 
            href="https://twitter.com" 
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="px-6 py-3 bg-white text-blue-600 font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors"
          >
            Bi Mu a Twitter
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</MainLayout>
